item.title: [317]GS spec's [317]
item.dc:creator: @Sideways_8 Sideways_8
item.description:
@Sideways_8 wrote:

Well, to start, go into the Special.java and add the item id’s of the GodSword/Weapons you want to spec, then go into the Client.java and search for “5698” and it should have a special section for the dragon dagger, under the last } hit enter, start a new line, I reccomend copying and pasting the dragon dagger special and then just changing the GFX/Damage Bonus/Item IDs.
